### ============================================================
###  CINEK — API Test File (IntelliJ HTTP Client / VS Code REST Client)
###  Base URL: http://localhost:8080
###  Seed accounts: admin/Admin@123  |  testuser/User@123
### ============================================================

@base = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken = <paste_admin_token_here>
@userToken  = <paste_user_token_here>

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  1. AUTH
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1a. Login as ADMIN (copy token → @adminToken above)
POST {{base}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 1b. Login as USER (copy token → @userToken above)
POST {{base}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "User@123"
}

### 1c. Register new account
POST {{base}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser",
  "email": "newuser@test.com",
  "password": "NewUser@123",
  "fullName": "New User"
}

### 1d. Refresh access token
POST {{base}}/api/auth/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 1e. Validate token
GET {{base}}/api/auth/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 1f. Logout (blacklists both tokens)
POST {{base}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "<paste_refresh_token_here>"
}


### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  2. MOVIES (public read, admin write)
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 2a. List all movies (page 1, size 10)
GET {{base}}/api/movies?page=1&size=10

### 2b. Search by keyword
GET {{base}}/api/movies?keyword=inception

### 2c. Filter by genre
GET {{base}}/api/movies?genre=Sci-Fi

### 2d. Get movie by ID
GET {{base}}/api/movies/1

### 2e. Trending movies
GET {{base}}/api/movies/trending?limit=5

### 2f. Create movie (ADMIN only)
POST {{base}}/api/movies
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Dune: Part Two",
  "description": "Paul Atreides dẫn dắt người Fremen chống lại Harkonnen.",
  "genre": "Sci-Fi",
  "duration": 166,
  "releaseYear": 2024,
  "posterUrl": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2QyZGU4ZDctOWMzMy00NTc5LThlOGQtODhmNDI1NjgwZjc0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMDM2NDM2MQ@@._V1_SX300.jpg",
  "director": "Denis Villeneuve",
  "actors": "Timothée Chalamet, Zendaya, Rebecca Ferguson"
}

### 2g. Update movie (ADMIN only)
PUT {{base}}/api/movies/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Inception",
  "description": "Updated description.",
  "genre": "Sci-Fi",
  "duration": 148,
  "releaseYear": 2010,
  "posterUrl": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjAxMzY3NjcxNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTI5OTM0Mw@@._V1_SX300.jpg",
  "director": "Christopher Nolan",
  "actors": "Leonardo DiCaprio, Joseph Gordon-Levitt"
}

### 2h. Delete movie (ADMIN, soft-delete)
DELETE {{base}}/api/movies/16
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  3. WATCH HISTORY & VIDEO STREAMING
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 3a. Save watch progress (upsert)
POST {{base}}/api/history
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movieId": 1,
  "progress": 45
}

### 3b. Save more progress on another movie
POST {{base}}/api/history
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movieId": 3,
  "progress": 72
}

### 3c. Save progress for 3rd movie
POST {{base}}/api/history
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movieId": 7,
  "progress": 30
}

### 3d. Continue watching list
GET {{base}}/api/history/continue?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 3e. Stream video by movie ID (returns 206 Partial Content)
GET {{base}}/api/videos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Range: bytes=0-1048575

### 3f. Get video playback info
GET {{base}}/api/movies/1/playback
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}


### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  4. REVIEWS
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 4a. Add review for movie 1 (as testuser)
POST {{base}}/api/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movieId": 1,
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Xuất sắc! Một trong những bộ phim hay nhất tôi từng xem."
}

### 4b. Add review for movie 2
POST {{base}}/api/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movieId": 2,
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Heath Ledger đóng Joker quá tuyệt vời!"
}

### 4c. Add review for movie 7
POST {{base}}/api/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movieId": 7,
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Classic Sci-Fi, ảnh hưởng cả thế hệ."
}

### 4d. Get reviews of movie 1
GET {{base}}/api/movies/1/reviews?page=0&size=10

### 4e. Delete review (owner hoặc ADMIN)
DELETE {{base}}/api/reviews/1
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}


### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  5. RECOMMENDATIONS (Neo4j graph)
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 5a. Get recommendations for testuser (userId=2)
### Cần xem/review vài phim trước để có collaborative filtering
GET {{base}}/api/recommendations/2?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}


### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  6. USER PROFILE
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 6a. Get own profile
GET {{base}}/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 6b. Update profile
PUT {{base}}/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Test User Updated",
  "avatarUrl": "https://i.pravatar.cc/150?u=testuser"
}

### 6c. Change password
POST {{base}}/api/users/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "User@123",
  "newPassword": "NewPass@456",
  "confirmPassword": "NewPass@456"
}

### 6d. Check username available
GET {{base}}/api/users/check-username/admin

### 6e. Check email available
GET {{base}}/api/users/check-email/admin@cinek.dev

### 6f. Admin: activate user account
POST {{base}}/api/users/activate/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  7. HEALTH CHECK
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 7a. Actuator health
GET {{base}}/actuator/health
